sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant MC as scheduler
    participant CE as cmd_encoder
    participant WD as wdata_path
    participant DM as dfi_master
    participant PHY as PHY

    Note over MC,PHY: T = cycle index relative to WR command issue

    MC->>CE: cycle 0: issue WR (bank, col)
    CE->>DM: cycle 1: drive (cs_n=0, ras_n=1, cas_n=0, we_n=0)
    DM->>PHY: cycle 1: WR on dfi_address, dfi_bank

    Note over WD: countdown CWL cycles

    MC->>WD: cycle 0: alert (AXI ID, burst_len)
    WD->>WD: cycle 1..CWL: pull beats from AXI W FIFO

    WD->>DM: cycle CWL+1: drive dfi_wrdata_en=1
    WD->>DM: cycle CWL+1: drive dfi_wrdata (beat 1)
    WD->>DM: cycle CWL+2: drive dfi_wrdata (beat 2)
    Note over WD,DM: ... up to BL beats
    WD->>DM: cycle CWL+BL: drive dfi_wrdata (last beat)
    WD->>DM: cycle CWL+BL+1: dfi_wrdata_en=0

    DM->>PHY: write data train delivered

    Note over MC: cycle 0+ε: B response issued to AXI (posted-write semantics)
